Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.88,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(775,599)}Epizoda 4:\N "Královna noci"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.37,0:24:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piškot se šlehačkou. Houska.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah—
